description: Lavazza Expression is where you can experience the quality of Italy’s best-known coffee. A place where genuine flavours, creativity and an eye for design converge. name: Café Monsieur Croque
description: A croque monsieur is a baked or fried boiled ham and cheese sandwich. The dish originated in ... croquer ("to bite, to crunch") and the word monsieur ("mister"). The sandwich's first recorded appearance on a Paris café menu was in 1910 and we want to bring the taste of Paris here in the Airport.

name: Jaipur Indian Food
description: Our dishes are never short of flavor and use a variety of aromatic and fiery spices to ensure all of our food is served with real personality and authentic charm only ever found on the streets of India and in the recipe books of generations gone before.

name: Costa Café
description: Costa coffee was first poured on our shores in 1971 at 9 Newport Street, London, by Sergio and Bruno Costa. Today, just a few metres away from where they first set up, the Costa Roastery produces the same unique Mocha Italia blend that the Costa brothers worked so hard to create.

name: Cafe Ritazza
description: Each and every Caffè Ritazza coffee bean is hand-picked for optimum quality assurance, and then carefully developed and tailored into blends that match the local taste and cultures of each worldwide location.

name: Brioche Dorée
description: Discover Brioche Dorée, an urban Café-bakery that has combined French tradition and exceptional quality products in a quick-service setting for almost 40 years, internationally. Brioche Dorée is set in a French country atmosphere that captivates customers with the authentic fresh aromas of bread and pastry baking. Guests will enjoy an array of hand-made sandwiches, healthy garden salads, artisan breads gourmet pastries and custom roasted coffees.

Guests can enjoy a range of freshly baked pastries, sandwiches and plenty of international dishes like Beef with Oyster sauce and Buttered chicken with rice.

Trib's mission is to sell delicious and remarkable food and beverage to match our world class locations, to consistently provide our customers with impeccable service by demonstrating warmth, graciousness, efficiency, knowledge, professionalism and integrity to our work. To have every customer who comes through our door greeted or acknowledged within 20 seconds, and thanked at least once for allowing us to serve, and to leave impressed.
